      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels so pointless though. like i'm just dragging this heavy weight around every single day for no reason. if he's gone, then the part of me that actually lived is gone too. i'm just a shell. what's the point of fighting to stay in a world where nothing makes sense anymore? it feels like i'm just being cruel to myself by staying here.",
